snippet: With Andre Johnson sidelined, the rookie DeAndre Hopkins pulled in a 3-yard touchdown pass from Matt Schaub to give the Texans an overtime win over the Titans.
abstract: Football Roundup; Houston Texans beat Tennessee Titans, 30-24, in overtime; other NFL scores noted.
lead_paragraph: With Andre Johnson sidelined, the rookie DeAndre Hopkins pulled in a 3-yard touchdown pass from Matt Schaub to give the Texans an overtime win over the Titans.

headline.print_headline: With Top Option Out, Texans Win on Catch by Rookie
